M|Use |tx|rc DOM provides APIs to hint the browser abt resources it will need. These are esp useful in server cp to start loading resources before the client even receives the HTML.
M|Use |- **|Resolve DNS for a domain you expect to connect to
M|Use |- **|Establish connection (DNS + TCP + TLS) to a server
M|Use |- **|Fetch a resource (stylesheet, font, script, im) you'll use soon
M|Use |- **|Fetch an ES md you'll use soon
M|Use |- **|Fetch and evaluate a stylesheet or script
M|Use |- **|Fetch and evaluate an ES md
M|Use |**Ex|**
