M|Use |**Wh|**
M|Use |tx|\| ap \| Use case \|
M|Use |tx|\|-----\|----------\|
M|Use |tx|\| `prefetchDNS` \| Third-party domains you'll connect to later \|
M|Use |tx|\| `preconnect` \| APIs or CDNs you'll fetch from immediately \|
M|Use |tx|\| `preload` \| ct resources needed for current page \|
M|Use |tx|\| `preloadModule` \| JS modules for likely nx navigation \|
M|Use |tx|\| `preinit` \| Stylesheets/scripts that must execute early \|
M|Use |tx|\| `preinitModule` \| ES modules that must execute early \|
